{"tid":908460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國前總理:勿把中國妖魔化 中德應緊密合作","createTime":"2018-11-19T14:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T15:52:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"817fd7a51acd1cff1f0ff487279caa1fd6803ca8","tid":908460,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/11/19/1995339_eaee0edd1167fbe81d970dd98d2444de_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F11%2F19%2F1995339_eaee0edd1167fbe81d970dd98d2444de_320.jpg&h=3cf5b35a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國前總理施羅德(Gerhard Schroder)警告德國勿把中國妖魔化，稱面對美國總統特朗普的貿易威脅，中德兩大經濟強國應該更加緊密地合作。<br />\n施羅德稱，中國和德國有着共同利益。他指，那些被源於美國的衝突所影響的國家，必須更加緊密地站在一起。德國不能淪為美中貿易戰的一部分。<br />\n外界預計，德國很快就會降低政府審查外資投資的門檻。歐盟成員國則正在敲定一項協定，確保對這類投資進行更嚴密的檢查。<br />\n施羅德質疑這種做法，他反對把華為等中國企業排除在德國下一代流動網絡建設之外。<br />\n施羅德於2002年連任成功的原因之一，就是他堅決反對美國出兵伊拉克的立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1995339/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%89%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%3A%E5%8B%BF%E6%8A%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A6%96%E9%AD%94%E5%8C%96+%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%B7%E6%87%89%E7%B7%8A%E5%AF%86%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1995339%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2590%2586%253A%25E5%258B%25BF%25E6%258A%258A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A6%2596%25E9%25AD%2594%25E5%258C%2596%2B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%25B7%258A%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C&d=ayxGCzeFtYLQTdJ4vPfzY7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b7d06fc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1995339/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%89%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%3A%E5%8B%BF%E6%8A%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A6%96%E9%AD%94%E5%8C%96+%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%B7%E6%87%89%E7%B7%8A%E5%AF%86%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C</a>"},{"pid":"fdf491f1d9